<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٤٢٥ <span class="c2">(م)</span> - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6952">يَحْيَى بْنُ بُكَيْرٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5348">اللَّيْثُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7248">يُونُسَ </a>بِهَذَا،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَعَ أَبِي خُزَيْمَةَ الْأَنْصَارِيِّ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>